*Izgledati* je kao da će kiša padati. (It looks like it's going to rain.)

Ona *izgleda* mlađe nego što jeste. (She looks younger than she is.)

*Izgledalo* je da će on biti kasno. (It looked like he was going to be late.)

Ona se *izgledala* užasno. (She looked awful.)

*Izgledam* li umoran? (Do I look tired?)